data.description: Come see this beautifully maintained one-owner 2-story home with attached Garage! Priced to sell! The main floor features a spacious great room that connects to the dining room and kitchen. Also, on the main floor is a half bath and laundry room. The 2nd floor features the owner's suite with walk-in closet and private bathroom. Additionally, upstairs are 2 other bedrooms, another full bath and a loft.
